{"tid":1558844,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港文革] 港共企圖在香港重演文革悲劇","createTime":"2019-09-10T14:59:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:47:22.000Z","uid":65072,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e120819681979aedf1eef8271f3f1295fba7d3","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T14:59:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共又再煽動民眾鬥民眾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n而家休班警當街執法<br />\n異見人士上趙被打被批鬥<br />\n藍屍廢老拎正牌打人<br />\n黑警再之後補飛話whatapps有人報案<br />\n企圖合理化件事<br />\n文革慘劇將會在港再上演<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港再無法治<br />\n大家要記住呢班歴史罪人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9357c9af3af261da19523cd18088862cecfa6bfc","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:00:07.000Z","msg":"垃圾港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1018358764e8be24d06c87609df063b9fdfdd1d","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:00:34.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"77f287ccd1b8e110fffe46bad13237ad9dc62d84","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:02.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"83269dbcdaf2d958adf74cd62ed035ffbb0dec53","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"2d0105c24cce65eb042cec0c9a2ee07d0ba90968","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:01:49.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"ba99da5117cf96762432b989c2b4b0118489168d","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:02:13.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"cf8f155014a4ada7107a656bbe1def664858906a","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:02:34.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"f577e1dc2df1fe6b71b937eac5064978e621b9a0","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:02:51.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"bc1510e2d0dd147a4801fe18c807c36814421a8e","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:04.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"7641b392a11fd7cfcc26e4b5a240bc448e0941bc","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:19.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"8c38e0242495cd5e949237ffc85b55121e126672","tid":1558844,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，群眾鬥群眾，拉一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當然90%都係三毛，有時又話同你對話實際上要你答應某大前提嘅條件，但亦都唔排除有真心膠中計信咗佢地一套，所謂拉一派打一派，群眾鬥群眾就係咁，要你自相殘殺，孤立主要敵人，然後共匪就可以輕鬆逐個擊破，普羅大眾應該要明白呢一點，無論如何都唔可以比三毛成功分化<br />\n<br />\n一個社會運動總會有犯錯嘅時候，可貴之處係反省，吸取教訓，下一次可以做得更好，向運動嘅成功邁進一步，而唔係中咗共匪嘅分化計，變成互相指罵，<span style=\"color: red;\">2014年雨革因示威者內部分裂而亡，切記歷史教訓，和理非同埋勇武必須同心合作，互相掩護</span><br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n#五大訴求缺一不可<br />\n#永不割蓆，永不分化，保持改進"},{"pid":"2946da005cb2677581cad97b5d85c215d0315ddd","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:46.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"bc616fa0dc4c90f6c271f5bcd4ceb6d0f6725759","tid":1558844,"uid":65072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c38e0242495cd5e949237ffc85b55121e126672","tid":1558844,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T15:03:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">［抗分化］共匪宜家玩緊老技倆，群眾鬥群眾，拉一派打一派</span></span><br />\n<br />\n共匪一貫手法，分化、滲透，然後拉籠一派打一派，政府有時會軟硬兼施，打下感情牌博同情，亦會派三毛做打手，屌/笑/鬧/玩膠嗰啲當